.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, cain, dannemann, oliveros
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, goldfish
4 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, go, whist
 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the goldfish is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the old-henry-smoker is between the oliveros-smoker and the person drinking cola##2
 8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5
 9. the owner of the dog is the oliveros-smoker##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola       | almond-milk | tea     | iced-tea     |
| Cigar   | cain      | old-henry       | oliveros | dannemann |
| Pet           | frog       | goldfish    | dog     | bird         |
| Game     | whist | go     | canasta     | monopoly       |

