.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, plum, pumpkin, radish
City: nizza, rome, berlin, london
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, davidoff, baccarat, chaman
4 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, pony, turtle
 1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 3. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the davidoff-smoker##5
 4. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
 5. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is between the chaman-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##2
 7. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 9. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
11. the person traveling to berlin is the owner of the dog##1
12. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | radish    | pumpkin      | plum   | apricot |
| City   | nizza | berlin | rome | london  |
| Cigar   | davidoff   | baccarat         | alhambra  | chaman  |
| Pet           | pony      | dog          | turtle | lizard  |

