.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, mirinda, sprite
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, cain, tiparillo, game
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, metal, pop, reggae
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, martial-arts, disaster, sports
 1. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5
 2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is between the fan of metal and the person drinking sprite##2
 8. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the fan of pop is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
13. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola     | mirinda        | sprite      |
| Cigar           | cain    | game   | tiparillo | siglo |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | metal    | country        | pop         |
| Movie-Genre         | musical    | disaster | sports         | martial-arts    |

