The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, dubstep, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, surfing, lacrosse, weightlifting
 1. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
 2. the fan of techno is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
 4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the fan of dubstep##1
10. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
11. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
12. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |      4       |
| Flower         | iris | lily    | marigold | bellflower  |
