The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, lily, begonia, daisy
 1. the journalist is between the person who's sport is handball-polo and the person eating plum##2
 2. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5
 3. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
 4. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
 5. the person eating plum is the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 7. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
 8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 9. the chef is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
10. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
12. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball-polo##5
13. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Sport      | handball-polo             | surfing       | handball    | skateboarding       |
| Food          | papaya             | peach      | plum     | grapes    |
