 9. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
10. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
12. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
13. the person watching epic movies is the person eating broccoli##1

