 2. the person eating banana is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 3. the polish is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the american##2
 4. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the american##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 7. the australian is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
 9. the australian is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
10. the polish is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
12. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | sprite          |
| Food          | lime    | radish        | potato     | banana          |
| Nationality           | brazilian | australian        | polish | american |
| Flower   | sunflower    | balloon-flower     | amaryllis      | poppy        |

