.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, swimming, badminton, cricket
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, doctor, journalist, musician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, thriller, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, soul, trance, ambient
 1. the fan of soul is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 3. the musician is on the left or right of the architect##3
 4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 5. the doctor is between the journalist and the person watching zombie movies##2
 6. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the journalist is the person watching disaster movies##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
10. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
11. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the architect##1
13. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Sport      | badminton   | cricket      | swimming | soccer     |
| Job           | musician   | architect  | doctor        | journalist |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | zombie     | thriller      | disaster   |
| Music-Genre     | soul | trance | ambient          | r&b     |

