.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose, lily, daffodil
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, drama, martial-arts
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, skydiving, magic-tricks
 1. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who growsbegonia##1
 3. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 7. the social-worker is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person who growslily##5
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaffodil##5
12. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Flower          | begonia | lily  | daffodil    | rose       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | drama   | martial-arts  | action     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks      | skydiving    | gardening        | card-games |

 